Class SessionAuthentication

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jetty.security.authentication.LoginAuthenticator.UserAuthenticationSucceeded
org.eclipse.jetty.security.authentication.SessionAuthentication
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, AuthenticationState, AuthenticationState.Succeeded, Request.AuthenticationState, Session.ValueListener
public class SessionAuthentication extends LoginAuthenticator.UserAuthenticationSucceeded implements Serializable, Session.ValueListener
When a user has been successfully authenticated with some types of Authenticator, the Authenticator stashes a SessionAuthentication into an HttpSession to remember that the user is authenticated.
